properties.info: Tiger Sharks, or “Sea Tigers” as they are sometimes called, are a kind of shark that can grow up to 5 meters in length (twice the size of the average adult human). They are most known for their diets as they eat a range of sea creatures including fish, seals, dolphins, squids, and other sharks. They have also been known to digest trash that they find in the ocean.
